# Architecture Diagram Source

Regenerate `public/architecture.png` with these corrections:

- Use **project** instead of **ecosystem** throughout
- `refreshAllEcosystems` → `refreshAllProjects`
- `fetchSingleEcosystemUncached` → `fetchSingleProjectUncached`
- Route: `GET /api/issues/[project]` (not `[ecosystem]`)

## Mermaid Reference

```mermaid
flowchart TB
    subgraph Client [CLIENT]
        UI[Issues UI]
        SWR[useIssuesFetch / SWR]
    end

    subgraph ReadPath [READ PATH]
        API[/api/issues]
        getCache[getIssuesFromCache]
    end

    subgraph RefreshPath [REFRESH PATH]
        GA[GitHub Actions]
        Cron[/api/cron/refresh]
        Refresh[refreshAllProjects]
        Fetch[fetchSingleProjectUncached]
        Normalize[normalize]
        Status[status]
        Readiness[readiness]
    end

    Redis[(Upstash Redis)]
    GitHub[GitHub API]

    UI --> SWR
    SWR --> API
    API --> getCache
    getCache -->|read only| Redis

    GA -->|daily| Cron
    Cron --> Refresh
    Refresh --> Fetch
    Fetch -->|fetch| GitHub
    GitHub -->|raw| Normalize
    Normalize --> Status --> Readiness
    Readiness -->|normalized| Redis
```
